<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>9</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/general_styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/puzzle_styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-lightgreen-frame">Home</a>
        <form action="/logout" method="get">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lightgreen-frame btn-logout">Log out</button>
        </form>
    </nav>
    <div class="container-supremeth">
        <div class="question-wrapper">
            <div class="poem-wrapper">
                <p class="poem">Sara pe deal buciumul suna cu jale,<br/>
                Turmele-l urc, stele le scapara-n cale,<br/>
                Apele plang, clar izvorand in fantane;<br/>
                Sub un salcam, draga, m-astepti tu pe mine.</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="question">Ce mesaj a vrut sa transmita poetul catre cititor in aceste versuri?</h2><!--criptat cu ceva-->
            <div class="form-wrapper">
                <form action="/puzzles/9" method="post">
                    <% if(progress > pageIndex) { %>
                        <input type="text" name="answer" id="answer" disabled>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lightgreen" disabled>Submit</button>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <input type="text" name="answer" id="answer">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lightgreen">Submit</button>
                    <% } %>
                </form>
                <div class="form-footer">
                    <p>&gt;&gt;&gt;<%= message || "" %></p>
                    <% if(progress > pageIndex) { %>
                        <a href="/puzzles/10" class="btn btn-lightgreen">Purcede</a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>